  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK358">
<l>piṟappeṉṉum pētaimai nīṅkac ciṟappeṉṉuñ</l>
<l>cemporuḷ kāṇpa taṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>True knowledge consists in the removal of ignorance; which is (the cause of) births, and the perception of the True Being who is (the bestower of) heaven.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
